    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《时光列车》是一款简单却极富挑战性的解谜游戏，你需要在时间和空间中规划列车路线。操控时间，制造因果混乱，挑战 50 个令人费解的谜题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/1b30574941d95b9cf4e4e30ca6bf9a09.poster.avif?t=1738369667\" width=800 height=546 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/1b30574941d95b9cf4e4e30ca6bf9a09.webm?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/1b30574941d95b9cf4e4e30ca6bf9a09.mp4?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个传送门上方的数字表示它会将列车送回或送往多少时间。要完成关卡，你需要铺设轨道，让时光列车收集散布在谜题区域内的所有奖杯。但请小心，致命陷阱会摧毁列车，除非你能在正确的时间解除它们……而这个正确的时间可能是在过去，也可能是在未来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/807fbfee088709a8145a31d27c5544c9.poster.avif?t=1738369667\" width=800 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/807fbfee088709a8145a31d27c5544c9.webm?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289480/extras/807fbfee088709a8145a31d27c5544c9.mp4?t=1738369667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
